<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us - The Current</title>
    <!-- Load Tailwind CSS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- Load Inter font -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700;900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <!-- Configure Tailwind to use the sans-serif font -->
    <script>
      tailwind.config = {
        theme: {
          extend: {
            fontFamily: {
              sans: ["Inter", "sans-serif"],
            },
          },
        },
      };
    </script>
  </head>
  <body class="font-sans bg-gray-50 text-gray-900">
    <!-- Header Navigation -->
    <nav class="bg-white shadow-sm sticky top-0 z-50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center h-16">
          <!-- Logo -->
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-600">The Current</span>
          </div>
          <!-- Navigation Links -->
          <div class="hidden sm:ml-6 sm:flex sm:space-x-8">
            <a
              href="/"
              class="inline-flex items-center px-1 pt-1 border-b-2 border-transparent text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 hover:border-gray-300 hover:text-gray-700"
            >
              Home
            </a>
            <a
              href="/about"
              class="inline-flex items-center px-1 pt-1 border-b-2 border-indigo-500 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900"
            >
              About
            </a>
            <a
              href="/topics"
              class="inline-flex items-center px-1 pt-1 border-b-2 border-transparent text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 hover:border-gray-300 hover:text-gray-700"
            >
              Topics
            </a>
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="inline-flex items-center px-1 pt-1 border-b-2 border-transparent text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 hover:border-gray-300 hover:text-gray-700"
            >
              Contact
            </a>
            <a
              href="/create"
              class="inline-flex items-center px-1 pt-1 border-b-2 border-transparent text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 hover:border-gray-300 hover:text-gray-700"
            >
              Create Post
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Page Header -->
    <header class="bg-white shadow-sm">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
          About The Current
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl">
          We believe in the power of great ideas. Our mission is to provide
          clear, insightful commentary on the topics that shape our world.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <!-- Our Story Section -->
        <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Our Story</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
              "The Current" was started in 2024 as a small project to track the
              fast-moving trends in technology. We quickly realized that
              technology doesn't exist in a vacuum. It's deeply intertwined with
              design, and both are reflections of our broader culture.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
              Our blog expanded to cover all three pillars, with a focus on
              delivering high-quality, well-researched articles that respect our
              readers' time and intelligence. We are not about clickbait; we are
              about conversation.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-0">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
              Our mission is simple: to make sense of the complex. We aim to be
              a reliable source for anyone curious about the "why" behind the
              "what."
            </p>
            <ul
              class="mt-4 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside text-lg text-gray-600"
            >
              <li>To analyze, not just report.</li>
              <li>To explore nuances, not just headlines.</li>
              <li>To build a community of curious minds.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Team Section -->
        <div class="mt-24">
          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 text-center"
          >
            Meet the Team
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center text-xl text-gray-600">
            We're a small, dedicated group of writers and thinkers.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-12 grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
            <!-- Team Member 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Alex Johnson</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-base font-medium text-indigo-600">
                Founder & Lead Technology Editor
              </p>
              <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
                With a background in software engineering, Alex writes about the
                future of AI, development, and the tech industry's cultural
                impact.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Team Member 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Maria Garcia</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-base font-medium text-indigo-600">
                Senior Design Contributor
              </p>
              <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
                Maria is a UX/UI designer who explores the principles of
                minimalism, user-centric design, and the intersection of art and
                utility.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Team Member 3 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">David Kim</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-base font-medium text-indigo-600">
                Culture & Media Analyst
              </p>
              <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
                David covers the creator economy, remote work, and the shifting
                trends in how we live, work, and connect with each other.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-gray-800 mt-16">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-base text-gray-400">
          &copy; 2025 The Current. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
